descriptionHtml:
This is an .exe application that  requires no installation and can be used while offline. It allows you to see all the ingredients in a list, search for a particular ingredient and search for the ingredients that have a particular effect. When searching for an ingredient it will show you the weight, value, the four effects, a list of the ingredients that share the effect and locations where the ingredient can be found. This allows for easy combination of your ingredients without the need to waste them trying to figure out effects!

You can catch up with more information and leave comments at blog.andrearedhead.com.

